title: Lotus Leaf Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Organic, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Provides meals made with wholesome ingredients. Menu is vegetarian and gluten-free friendly; dishes are marked if can be made vegan. Beverages choices include smoothies, juices, wheat grass, and organic wine. In 2014 relocated from 613 A W Douglas Ave.
